Become a Sugaring NYC ambassador. We are looking for authentic, fashion-forward Instagram influencers to join our Collaboration Program. Try sugaring service by your own, share your experince with your audince, participate in giveaways,story take overs, Q&A’s and fun collaborations.

To apply – simply DM @sugaringNYC on Instagram
